## Microsoft Graph API Permissions

The following client `application` permissions are needed in order to use this {{.Type | lower}}:

**Required:**
- `WindowsUpdates.ReadWrite.All`

**Optional:**
- `None` `[N/A]`

## Dependency Notes

This resource requires an existing `microsoft365_graph_beta_windows_updates_autopatch_updatable_asset_group` resource. The `updatable_asset_group_id` attribute must reference the ID of that group.

## Field Mutability

| Field | Mutable after creation |
|-------|------------------------|
| `updatable_asset_group_id` | No — changes require resource replacement |
| `entra_device_ids` | Yes — devices can be added or removed in-place |

